                                                <p><name type="person"><hi rend="initialcap">B</hi>REMER, <hi rend="initialcap">L</hi>UDWIG</name>, Private, <name type="organization">Co. C, 45th
                                                                Pennsylvania</name>, aged 45 years.   <name type="BATTLE" key="58">Petersburg</name>, <date type="injury" when="1865-04-02">April 2d,
                                                                                1865</date>.   Fracture of right parietal by conoidal ball.  Corps and <name type="place" key="WASHINGTON">Washington</name> hospitals.   Removal of
                                                                fragments of depressed bone, <date type="operation" when="1865-04-08">April 8th</date>.   Death, <date type="death" when="1865-04-12">April 12th, 1865</date>. </p>                                                
